<a id="comment-9711"></a>
<div class="comment">
 <h3 class="title"><a href="node/977#comment-9711" class="active">Relationship</a></h3>
 <div class="content"><p >In a lazy language, there are 2-3 events in every values lifetime: thunk creation (via evaluation), thunk reduction (via forcing) - which may or may not occur, and thunk abandonment (via garbage collection).</p></div>
 <div class="links">By <a href="user/97" title="View user profile.">Tim Sweeney</a> at Mon, 09/19/2005 - 23:23 | <a href="user/login">login</a> or <a href="user/register">register</a> to post comments</div>
